The Forest Stewardship Council

The Forest Stewardship Council (FSC) supports responsible forestry, which is a vital solution to combat climate change. Choosing FSC-certified products – whether furniture, building materials, paper, rubber, or textiles – helps protect forests, wildlife, clean water and supports the Indigenous Peoples, forest workers and communities who depend on them. Choosing FSC-certified products can also help to mitigate climate change by supporting responsible management of the world’s forests. For a better future, choose FSC.

About this item

  • 👍【Military Standard Quality & 100 Day+ Ultra-Long Life Battery】- The frame of the military smart watch for men is made from a special aluminum alloy material,successfully passed 12 military tests, is rugged, waterproof, dustproof, and can handle all the extreme environments.with a battery capacity of up to 900mAh, 5 times of traditional smartwatches. Offers 100 days standby time and 30 days for daily usage, say goodbey to frequent charge, no more need to bring so much cables for long trip!
  • 👍【LED Flashlight & Compass Adventures & 2 Pack Watch Straps 】- Tactical smart watches for men have a LED flashlight( Lighting range up to 6-10m). Equipped with a compass device, magnetically resistant, designed for professional outdoor exercise.You can take on any adventure no matter day or night. Definitely a great companion for your adventures! Also equipped with 2 comfortable and skin-friendly wristbands (silicone strap and nylon strap), the length can be adjusted freely. Users with sensitive skin can use the nylon strap.
  • 👍【2024 New Split Screen & 2.01" Big Screen & DIY Watch Faces】- We created a quick menu displayed on the split screen for the first time, and it updates in real time according to the user's latest visits, allowing you to use it more conveniently and intelligently. 2024 new Blackview W60 Smart Watch is equipped with 2.01"extra large HD full touch screen, TFT color display for outstanding HD quality. We offer you a variety of online dials, or you can also personalize the watch face by selecting your favorite photo (your family, pets, or other photos that you like).
  • 👍【Answer/Make Calls and AI Voice Assistant】Blackview fitness watch come with built-in HiFi stereo speakers and microphone. Once connected to Bluetooth, you can directly answer or make calls through the smartwatch. The "GloryFitPro" app stores multiple contacts, ensuring you stay connected with family and friends anytime, anywhere. Receive real-time notifications on the smartwatch for incoming calls or messages (WhatsApp, Facebook, Instagram, etc.). Speak to the AI voice assistant for quick help, such as weather forecast, making calls, setting alarms etc.
  • 👍【100+ Sports Modes】With more than 100 sports modes, this fitness tracker supports running, cycling, walking, climbing, yoga, skiing, football, and more. It tracks your daily data such as steps, time, distance, and calories, and connects to the GPS on your phone to record all your training routes and fitness using the "GloryFitPro" app to further motivate yourself to complete your exercise plan. It's an IP68 waterproof device that can meet your daily needs. (*NOTE: Not for sauna, hot water, swim, diving)
  • 👍【Monitor Health in Real Time】The fitness watch for women and men uses high-performance optical sensors to monitor dynamic heart rate in real time 24/7. It can also accurately track your personal sleep and detect blood oxygen saturation and stress levels to adjust your physical condition in a timely manner. The app even offers a detailed sleep quality analysis report (light/deep/awake sleep stage), helping you adjust your lifestyle towards a healthier lifestyle. (*NOTE: This watch cannot be used as a medical diagnostic tool.)
  • 👍【More Smart Tools】Apart from the features mentioned above, this smartwatch also offers other useful daily functions such as smart notifications, music control, camera control, weather forecast, sedentary reminders, alarm clock, stopwatch, timer, etc. Compatible with most Android 6.0 and iOS 9.0 or above smartphones.

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

I would believe it meant 100 days charge when idle and off the person, but what's the point of a watch when you don't use it? Some of the work outs are just duplicates of others just to inflate the amount of work outs branded.

        I do admit, there are some quality of life features I can't get enough of, such as a basic calculator, a flashlight and a decent alarm clock, but these features aren't enough trade-offs for the loss of quality of the product's main selling points.

        There are some things I am not considering, because of features I haven't used, like calling and contacts. That kinda goes to show the many niche uses.
